<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَخُرُوجُ الوَقْتِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَوُجُودُ المَاءِ إِنْ تَيَمَّمَ لِفَقْدِهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَزَوَالُ المُبِيحِ لَهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَخَلْعُ مَا يَمْسَحُ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> يُشْتَرَطُ لِكُلِّ مُتَنَجِّسٍ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- سَبْعُ غَسَلاتٍ إِنْ أَنْقَتْ، وَإِلَّا فَحَتَّى تُنْقِيَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- بِمَاءٍ طَهُورٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- مَعَ حَتٍّ وَقَرْصٍ لِحَاجَةٍ، إِنْ لَمْ يَتَضَرَّرِ المَحَلُّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَعَصْرٍ مَعَ إِمْكَانٍ فِيمَا تَشَرَّبَ، كُلَّ مَرَّةٍ خَارِجَ المَاءِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَكَوْنُ إِحْدَاهُا فِي مُتَنَجِّسٍ بِكَلْبٍ أَوْ خِنْزِيرٍ بِتُرَابٍ طَهُورٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَيَضُرُّ بَقَاءُ طَعْمٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- لَا لَوْنٍ، أَوْ رِيحٍ، أَوْ هُمَا عَجْزًا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيُجْزِئُ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فِي بَوْلِ غُلَامٍ لَمْ يَأْكُلْ طَعَامًا لِشَهْوَةٍ:</span> نَضْحُهُ، وَهُوَ غَمْرُهُ بِمَاءٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>